tedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"冇，唔好嘥錢<br />\n你幾多度？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7884d8febe498a1be207b552f11eaef73c8e5634","tid":2447971,"uid":79747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1d0def630371439c75c732cf8451c9f78e18c69","tid":2447971,"uid":268526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c363e3fe60339aff83f1cca5ef1ba87cd6bd804b","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"冇，唔好嘥錢<br />\n你幾多度？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T06:48:36.000Z","msg":"我廿幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:09:14.000Z","msg":"我都係，S型上彎十幾度，下彎廿幾度，中學嗰陣開始有，嗰陣要整個架每日戴住廿幾個鐘，醫生話唔會好得翻，戴架只會令你唔會惡化，所以戴咗一排之後都冇戴。<br />\n如果你十八歲以下，未發育完，去啪骨加keep住做矯正運動可能會直翻少少都未定。不過嗰陣一發現到自己有，睇過好多唔同嘅所謂脊醫，又去過睇物理治療師，都係冇改善到，所以我建議你都唔洗嘥錢去睇。<br />\n其實廿幾度唔算特別嚴重，所以唔洗做手術，就咁睇啲人睇唔出你有脊椎側彎。除咗有時行得耐企得耐會腰痛，基本上唔會影響到日常生活，所以好耐之前已經接受咗有呢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777b9a41b292624341b321fc18aac3d7c53f6b45","tid":2447971,"uid":159074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"有睇開一個<br />\n我自己係頸椎問題<br />\n做左幾次舒服左好多<br />\n佢話一開始要密D做 之後好返D可以唔洗咁密<br />\n差唔多要一半先會好<br />\n<br />\n同醫師好有緣 仲要平收我$200/次<br />\n出面搞起碼$500UP"},{"pid":"23d1b60b06a0957399d61d5d56d4c82cb4170277","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411158f796f737202404061976f31e5c2c48cf7c","tid":2447971,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:54:43.000Z","msg":"攪清楚成因先 , 肌肉唔平衡定係關節出事先"},{"pid":"b54d60098730209b7cb094cff8a870446ebfceeb","tid":2447971,"uid":268526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23d1b60b06a0957399d61d5d56d4c82cb4170277","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"平時企或者坐得耐就會開始痛<br />\n有時隻手會麻 唔知關唔關事"},{"pid":"0123c66bf503aaf053a5f461d311b3897613a935","tid":2447971,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"4575bd74c83b1203df13e6dc04ca440d4d8d0176","tid":2447971,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"其實d偏方<br />\n吊下吊下<br />\n又或者掛毛巾咁掛住自己<br />\n<br />\n係咪work"},{"pid":"548e08a130d174a7e8ce8c2c7be949293fe8dbc4","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4526733e0f9dcd6a1f0ff4fc51d341232864404d","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b54d60098730209b7cb094cff8a870446ebfceeb","tid":2447971,"uid":268526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23d1b60b06a0957399d61d5d56d4c82cb4170277","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"平時企或者坐得耐就會開始痛<br />\n有時隻手會麻 唔知關唔關事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:18:55.000Z","msg":"關事，我長期企會全身唔舒服尤其係彎度大既胸椎<br />\n手麻既話，你彎係彎邊面？如果向右彎，右手會麻痺都係症狀之一"},{"pid":"eaf1cf1f053e961eda39ec62573f3443478f7da3","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"548e08a130d174a7e8ce8c2c7be949293fe8dbc4","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4710bf2764d6cc210498c8b2438f7764af8b9b4","tid":2447971,"uid":268526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"548e08a130d174a7e8ce8c2c7be949293fe8dbc4","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"你六十幾度最後係咪去左做手術？<br />\n成日聽日講話游水有用 係咪真"},{"pid":"084daef4fed759fab782cb161943243c71065382","tid":2447971,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"777b9a41b292624341b321fc18aac3d7c53f6b45","tid":2447971,"uid":159074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"有睇開一個<br />\n我自己係頸椎問題<br />\n做左幾次舒服左好多<br />\n佢話一開始要密D做 之後好返D可以唔洗咁密<br />\n差唔多要一半先會好<br />\n<br />\n同醫師好有緣 仲要平收我$200/次<br />\n出面搞起碼$500UP"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3584ed4b9f377e201ecf00e638f0a86060d2f95","tid":2447971,"uid":382485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"有冇人知肋骨痛關唔關事呢樣事"},{"pid":"d1ef87e6d9c6c72c2e612bfd3ed68b3a7d81ed67","tid":2447971,"uid":358350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4710bf2764d6cc210498c8b2438f7764af8b9b4","tid":2447971,"uid":268526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"548e08a130d174a7e8ce8c2c7be949293fe8dbc4","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"你六十幾度最後係咪去左做手術？<br />\n成日聽日講話游水有用 係咪真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:01:24.000Z","msg":"真係有用架，我嗰陣時應該係中三暑假左右，去咗學游水，每星期唔知兩堂定三堂，而且每星期仲有跳舞拉筋(唔知關唔關事)，原本好似20幾度，一個暑假之後去複診，個醫生話我好咗好多，好似去返10幾度。但係暑假之後就冇再做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又去番20幾度。但係個醫生好似話16歲之後就會定型，所以都冇乜所謂。<br />\n所以如果係13 4歲發現，Keep住做運動應該會好轉"},{"pid":"1eecac4a35c8bef02ae2aa40405a1b1ff0951adc","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4710bf2764d6cc210498c8b2438f7764af8b9b4","tid":2447971,"uid":268526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"548e08a130d174a7e8ce8c2c7be949293fe8dbc4","tid":2447971,"uid":386420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"你六十幾度最後係咪去左做手術？<br />\n成日聽日講話游水有用 係咪真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"之後轉左睇脊醫，學左幾個施羅斯呼吸運動<br />\n下次覆診果陣回到五十幾度，不過之後都係卡係五十幾度左右<br />\n手術我本身想去台灣做，有個人專做脊彎手術做到好岀名，仲自創左一套手術技術，令到d人做完手術都保持到個柔韌度，可以做下運動<br />\n不過果位台灣名醫兩年前過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n游水個原理我諗都同鍛鍊全身肌肉差唔多，我之前都游過，不過始終都掌握唔到自由式，淨係識游蛙式，但游蛙式果陣會feel到自己發力唔平衡，驚會愈游愈差就冇游了"},{"pid":"9a115a418591f9a787605eb0470e0cd6105626a8","tid":2447971,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T21:38:36.000Z","msg":"冇得total啪正<br />\n只可改善孤度同唔再惡化落去"},{"pid":"18f2afe45618e61d74b0a49c6adcbc795e107c77","tid":2447971,"uid":271807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a87cba66cdd8e0a5e65c079f97c8376f1000885","tid":2447971,"uid":268526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"有冇ching試過整骨啪番正<br />\n成日上網見到但唔敢去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T21:41:01.000Z","msg":"睇係大彎定少彎，大彎基本無得救，祇可舒緩"}]}